So one thing came to mind.
SnOw OnO!
What a great choice indeed.
Such a choice I would high five myself.
SnOw OnO is a truck full of pure 808 shaved ice deliciousness.
I was hesitant to try SnOw OnO because Hawaiian Shaved Ice is possibly my favorite thing to eat when I am in Hawaii.
SnOw OnO did not disappoint!
I got the Onolicious (strawberry, blue Hawaiian, pineapple) with a snow cap on top.
Whats a snow cap you ask?
It is sweet condensed milk splashed on top of your shaved ice.
Don't knock it till you try it my friends.
