The girl that took my order was nice and gave me a stamp card with their social networking information.
Only gripe I had was that I had ALOT of syrup.
After just a minute or two I had a bit of a congealed mess, but it was hot out so it's not something that can be helped.
I'll definitely be back for more because there are so many other flavors to choose from.

